name: LILITH
description: The person I photographed is my mother and my mother is the strongest woman I have ever known in my life. She represents Lilith in mythology who is known as demonic female because she runs after her freedom and loved ones by resisting all kinds of restrictions and possessions. She rejects all adjectives from the male gaze. As in Lilith's story, she runs after her freedom and loved ones by resisting all kinds of restrictions and possessions. Lilith is my mother who made me who I am.
